{"tid":817313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最近生意好差，吹下水","createTime":"2018-09-13T09:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T14:19:01.000Z","uid":180557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"539e11b166ec065554161790cbff6164f3e34730","tid":817313,"uid":180557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"第一次經歷9月淡季，生意好差，平日可以得幾個客，唉，樓上樓下對面樓都係生意差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分享下在鋪頭人間觀察有趣事：<br />\n1）有枱8人客salaryman，4男4女，飲飲下酒，突然A男拎條好短的薯條咬住一邊，餵B男食，hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咀對咀，咀左落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 成班人立即大笑，d女話影唔切相，再嚟多次！ 結果佢地全部男就輪流玩呢個薯條遊戲，d女就好開心咁拍片影相。<br />\n<br />\n2）有枱6人客予約9:30，先來左3個西裝男，呀，一睇就知係合コン（聯誼）男1一坐低就同男2講：今夜絶対に持ち帰りたい！(今晚要打包囡囡！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後佢地就討論一陣點自我介紹，邊個做助攻。討論完，男3就同我講：我只會點ウーロンハイ(烏龍茶＋燒酒）但我酒量不好，可不可以只加好小量的酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈哈，當然可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3個囡囡都遲左15分鐘先到，仲要係casual look, t-shirt and jeans，不是合コン囡囡定番的ふわふわ感雪紡衫。<br />\n到中段，開始玩山手線game 炒熱左氣氛，打包男都明顯鎖定左目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n差不多12點，打包男：一陣去唱k，好不好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n囡囡：我要趕終電呀，你明天唔洗返工咩？ <br />\n打包男：我明天放假，大家一起去唱k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後，因為我要趕終電，所以趕佢地走，打包男就同d囡囡講：呢餐飯女生一人出2000円就可以。其實只係一人2980円，d男真係有＂風度＂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢地就好開心咁去唱K。<br />\n<br />\n仲有不少趣事，諗到再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8936700fc768c64f2c4215474431e3ecae061c34","tid":817313,"uid":48077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68faab5168c28dd0fa00714c3368efa3ac2bb0e7","tid":817313,"uid":191736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0a0d26ebdec08d682d309985f6d3784df70aead5","tid":817313,"uid":180557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"試過比客話我塩対応<br />\n又試過比客問我時給幾多，話我做得嘢，派咭片比我叫我去幫手<br />\n比客話對眼似某女藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e3380d88f0c4284cca43cd6d68508338a7b26e","tid":817313,"uid":25166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a0d26ebdec08d682d309985f6d3784df70aead5","tid":817313,"uid":180557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"試過比客話我塩対応<br />\n又試過比客問我時給幾多，話我做得嘢，派咭片比我叫我去幫手<br />\n比客話對眼似某女藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"塩対応 咩意思"},{"pid":"a54d418e7a7660d9c5c75dfe8c991b8b1d6a925d","tid":817313,"uid":53399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"樓主呢"}]}